<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Certificate</title>
    
    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400..900;1,400..900&display=swap');
      *{
          padding: 0;
          margin: 0;
          box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
          font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
      }

      .container {
          position: relative;
          
      }
      .bg-image {
        /* width: 100%; */
        height: 100vh
      }

      .text-container {
          position: absolute;
          top: 45%;
          padding:  0 13%;
          font-size: 16px;
          line-height: 26px;
          text-align: justify;
      }

      .line {
          height: 2px;
          width: 250px;
          display: block;
          background-color: black;
          margin: auto;
      }



      .author {
          display: flex;
          justify-content:space-between;
      }

      .signature-left {
          text-align: center;
          position: absolute;
          left: 20%;
          bottom: 20%
      }

      .signature-right {
          text-align: center;
          position: absolute;
          right: 20%;
          bottom: 20%
      }


      .name {
          font-size: 20px;
          margin-top: 8px;
      }


      .tag {
            position: absolute;
            top: 19.7%;
            right: 18.7% ;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            height: 40px;
            width: 40px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            
        }

    



    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <section class="container">
        <img class="bg-image" src="https://i.ibb.co/DDCF03y/cetificate.jpg" alt="">
        <div class="text-container">
            <p>This is to Certify that Mr/Ms.  <b> <%= studentDetails.name  %>  </b>, Son/Daughter of  <b> <%= studentDetails.fatherName  %>  </b>, , Hav Successfuly completed a course of 70 days traninng on   <b> <%= courseDetails.name  %>  </b>   powered by Jamalpur Zila Pariahad from 24th June to 6th November under the project of developing life skill and increasing awarness training activities for self development with obtained grade  <b> <%= mark %>  </b></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="signature-left">
                <div class="line"></div>
                <h5 class="name">(Mun Mun Jahan Liza)  </h5>
                <p>Chief Executive Officer</p>
                <p>Zilla Parishad, Jamalpur</p>
            </div>
            <div class="signature-right">
                <div class="line"></div>
                <h5 class="name">(Mun Mun Jahan Liza)  </h5>
                <p>Chief Executive Officer</p>
                <p>Zilla Parishad, Jamalpur</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tag">
            <h3><%= mark %> </h3>
        </div>


    </section>
</body>
</html>